# Catalog Category for NKP UI

All applications in this catalog must include the category **`dm-nkp-gitops-app-catalog`** in their `metadata.yaml` so users can find and filter apps from this custom catalog in the NKP UI.

## Rule

- In every `applications/<app>/<version>/metadata.yaml`, the `category` list **must** include:
  - **`dm-nkp-gitops-app-catalog`**
- Keep existing categories (e.g. `observability`, `security`, `ai-ml`); add this one in addition.
- When adding new apps (e.g. via `catalog-workflow.sh add-app`), add `dm-nkp-gitops-app-catalog` to the category list in the generated `metadata.yaml`.

## Example

```yaml
category:
  - dm-nkp-gitops-app-catalog
  - observability
  - monitoring
```

This allows the NKP UI to filter or group all apps sourced from the dm-nkp-gitops-app-catalog repository.
